title: Trinidad And Tobago Private Sector Credit
description: Private Sector Credit in Trinidad And Tobago decreased to 70991.40 TTD Million in August from 71014.90 TTD Million in July of 2022. Private Sector Credit in Trinidad And Tobago averaged 40006.32 TTD Million from 1995 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 71014.90 TTD Million in July of 2022 and a record low of 9882.10 TTD Million in March of 1995. This page provides - Trinidad And Tobago Private Sector Credit- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Trinidad and Tobago
